text:
"100% Confirmed" The Migos Jumped Sean Kingston In Vegas 2 hours ago share 
WSHH has confirmed what Twitter has been reporting, the Migos have jumped Sean Kingston out in Las Vegas. 
News of the incident are still unclear, but Twitter has been reporting live from the scene for the past few hours. 
Some sources are reporting that Quavo did try to stop the fight from happening. No word on the reason why the par trio was upset at the singer. 
Developing.
